Hungry Snake : Worms Zone
Welcome to
Hungry Snake: Worms Zone
! Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your information when you use our game.
1. Information We Collect
We do not collect any personal or sensitive information from users. Our game does not require registration, nor does it collect data such as names, email addresses, or physical locations.
2. Non-Personal Data
To improve gameplay and performance, the game may collect non-personal information such as:
Device type and operating system
Gameplay statistics (e.g., scores, level progress)
This data is collected anonymously and cannot identify individual users.
3. No Advertising
Our game is entirely ad-free. We do not display third-party advertisements or engage in ad tracking of any kind.
4. Third-Party Services
We do not integrate third-party services such as analytics tools or social media platforms that could collect or process your data.
5. Data Storage
All data related to your gameplay (e.g., scores and progress) is stored locally on your device. We do not store any data on external servers.
6. Children's Privacy
Our game is designed to be safe and enjoyable for players of all ages. Since we do not collect personal data, it complies with child protection regulations like COPPA and GDPR-K.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in the "Effective Date" at the top of this policy.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please feel free to contact us at
premiumqualityapps.com@gmail.com
